---
title: Lamb Rump & Spiced Roast Veggies with Jewelled Israeli Couscous & Yoghurt Dressing
description: Succulent lamb coupled with roasted baby carrots, pearl couscous and veggies, sit pretty together in this classic gourmet-style dinner. For the perfect finishing touch, we've added a delectable yoghurt dressing - never has a combination been so right!

*We’ve replaced the rainbow carrots in this recipe with peeled pumpkin pieces due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6604db2dfaa50670154dc0c7-04ddef5a.jpeg
